reviewText: 10 disc box set of movies from 1925 to 1939. Includes The Pleasure Garden '25, The Lodger '27, Downhill '27, The Man Who Knew Too Much, '34, The 39 Steps '35, Secret Agent '36, Sabotage '36, Young and Innocent '37, The Lady Vanishes '38, Jamaica Inn '39. The Lodger, The 39 Steps, Sabotage, Young and Innocent, The Lady Vanishes and Jamaica Inn have been digitally restored. Each movie has an introduction by Charles Barr.
